snippet.title: Worms: Reinforcements gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Worms: Reinforcements, Dos PC game produced by Team17 in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/worms-reinforcements/15592/
Worms: Reinforcements is a very nice strategy game, created in 1995. It is an action game can play the multiplayer. The game was simple and yet fun to play.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
